Title: SOMETHING BETTER SOMEWHER

reviewText: Boring. Stopped watching midway through second story. I expected funny since I rented it from the comedy section. And if not funny, some drama or action. Would have helped. But the drama and the acting were weak. I wish people would stop rating these boring movies so highly--this movie and The Station Agent were real duds. And they keep getting these 4-5 star ratings. At least it was free on Amazon Prime. Maybe I was missing something brilliant in the other hour of the movie I skipped.The first story is about the last day of a guy quitting his job. Everyone seems to like him but his boss. They show the leaving party where everyone gets drunk and says stuff they will probably regret tomorrow.
summary: Couldn't make it through the second story
Title: SOMETHING BETTER SOMEWHER
